snippet.title: Motorola C168i Mobile phone menu browse, ringtones, games, wallpapers
snippet.description:
Taking a look at this vintage mobile phone.

These videos are made for educational purposes and to preserve some footage of these devices that will disappear  in a few years.

Some of these phones are up for sale. If you are interested, take a look at my eBay page: https://www.ebay.co.uk/usr/blackberry_archive

Visit the Facebook group here: https://www.facebook.com/groups/659581635036466
